signatures.note:
Quire  marks are written in the upper margin of fols.
11r: ፪ “2”; 
14r: ፫ “3”; 
27r: ፬ “4”;
35r: ፭ “5”.

handDesc.handNote:
                        Hand a: very crude. Hand b: mediocre but regular
                        Black; red and reddish-brown (s. other details).
